snippet.title: Xolotl - Release Date Reveal
snippet.description:
Jump, dash, and swim in this epic adventure! Explore the vast Aztec lands in an axolotl action-platformer! Xolotl is a tough, 2D action-platformer, in which your goal is to regain your godly form and powers. Coming June 27!

Wishlist on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/18...

Follow on Instagram!
https://www.instagram.com/xolotlgame/
